      "rdf:value": "<L>26098<pc>2-1079<k1>Canda<k2>Canda\n{#Canda#}¦ (von 2. {#Cad, Cand#})\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) <lex>adj.</lex> {%gefällig, anlockend, einladend.%}\n<div n=\"3\"> α) <ab>parox.</ab>: {#a\\gnirhi jAni^ pU\\rvyaSCando\\ na sUro^ a\\rcizA^#}\n<ls>ṚV. 8,7,36.</ls> {#Sri\\ye Cando\\ na sma^yate viBA\\tI#}\n<ls n=\"ṚV.\">1,92,6.</ls>\n<div n=\"3\">— β) <ab>oxyt.</ab>: {#vezi^zWo\\ aNgi^rasA\\M yadDa\\ vipro\\ maDu^ cCa\\ndo Bana^ti re\\Ba i\\zwO#}\n<ls>ṚV. 6,11,3.</ls>\n<ls>SĀY.</ls> nimmt {#Candas#} als Thema an; <ab>vgl.</ab> {#maDucCanda, maDucCandas#} und\n<ls>NAIGH. 3,16</ls> {#Canda^H = stotA#}, wo das Wort mit Beziehung auf unsere Stelle aufgenommen, aber falsch betont sein kann.\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) <lex>m.</lex>\n<div n=\"2\"> a) {%Erscheinung, Aussehen, Gestalt%}: {#(prAsAdAH) kElAsamandaracCandA merucCandAstaTEva ca#}\n<ls>HARIV. 8359.</ls> {#taTA nAnAvayaSCandAstaTehAmfgarUpiRaH#}\n<ls n=\"HARIV.\">8360.</ls> {#prakrIqagaruqa˚#}\n<ls n=\"HARIV.\">8361.</ls> {#krOYca˚, gaja˚#},\n<ls n=\"HARIV.\">8362.</ls> <ab>Vgl.</ab> {#praticCanda, vicCanda#} .\n<div n=\"2\">— b) {%Lust, Gefallen an Etwas, Verlangen; Wille%}, = {#aBiprAya#} und {#vaSa#}\n<ls>AK. 3,3,20.</ls> <ls n=\"AK.\">3,4,16,91.</ls>\n<ls>H. 1383.</ls>\n<ls>an. 2,226.</ls>\n<ls>MED. d. 5.</ls> = {#aBilAza#}\n<ls>BHAR.</ls> zu <ls>AK.</ls> <ls>ŚKDR.</ls> {#mayocyamAnaM yadi te SrotuM CandaH#}\n<ls>R. 2,9,7.</ls> {#BaktacCanda#} {%Appetit%}\n<ls>SUŚR. 1,178,17.</ls> {#aBaktacCanda#}\n<ls n=\"SUŚR.\">2,18,10. 446,2.</ls> {#tatra syAtsvAminaSCandaH#} {%der Wille des Herrn%}\n<ls>YĀJÑ. 2,195.</ls> {#yastava cCandaH#} {%wie du willst%}\n<ls>VIKR. 38,13.</ls> {#yatra te CandastatrotTAsyanti vAjinaH#}\n<ls>MBH. 13,214.</ls> {#AsyatAM rucitaSCandaH kiM kAryaM bravIhi me#}\n<ls n=\"MBH. 13,\">1476.</ls> {#BavacCandaM samAjYAya nftyerannapsarogaRAH#}\n<ls n=\"MBH. 13,\">1422.</ls> {#avijYAya pituSCandam#}\n<ls>R. 3,4,50.</ls> <ls n=\"R.\">6,89,3.</ls> {#Cando nartayituryaTEva manasaH sfzwaM taTAsyA vapu